{"title":"绮","date":"2020-01-07T01:13:17.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 7, 2020","L":"01/07/2020","MM-DD":"01-07"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/07/nyzkUTQlq8be4YP.jpg","link":"2020/01/07/绮","comments":true,"tags":["他","梦"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-12-14T15:10:11.499Z","content":"<p>五色的蝴蝶在丛中飞舞<br>\n交错的巨大的巨颈<br>\n遮掩在盖大的叶片下<br>\n走入从中不觉惊慌</p>\n<p>尽头是红褐色的岩石<br>\n转身水已没过<br>\n绿色的茎叶格外鲜嫩</p>\n<p>纵身跳进湖中<br>\n双臂充满活力<br>\n跃出水面<br>\n旋即又回岩岸边</p>\n<p>轻快地在崎岖中穿梭<br>\n闪耀的碎片零落殆尽<br>\n睁开眼<br>\n窗前的人，窗外的雪</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>2020.01.07</em><br>\n<em>北京</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n","prev":{"title":"Promises第二章","link":"2020/01/09/PromisesChapter2"},"next":{"title":"Promises第一章","link":"2020/01/06/PromisesChapter1"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2020/01/07/绮/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Birch","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"December 14, 2020"},"reading_time":"116 words in 1 min"}